title: Focus &lrm;&ndash; Hamburger Concerto
description:
Hamburger Concerto is the fourth studio album by the progressive rock band Focus. 
 <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Focus_%28band%29" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Focus_%28band%29</a>

Released in 1974, it peaked at #20 on the UK charts. The title track is based on Variations on a Theme by Haydn by Johannes Brahms.
